2%80%99%20and%20bonds%20even%20among%20adversaries%20of%20diverse%20hues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBonds%20betoken%20trust%20and%20dependability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20purity%20of%20bonds%20between%20government%20and%20constitution%2C%C2%A0%20government%20and%20polity%2C%20institutions%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20media%20and%20truth-telling%2C%20between%20producers%20and%20consumers%2C%20officialdom%20and%20academic%20centres%2C%20banks%20and%20clients%2C%20judges%20and%20litigants%2C%20employers%20and%20employees%2C%20information%20givers%20and%20information%20seekers%2C%20establishment%20and%20public-spirited%20men%20and%20women%2C%20protesting%20citizens%20and%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20between%20toddlers%20and%20educators%E2%80%94all%20those%20bonds%20and%20more%E2%80%94determine%20the%20quality%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20ruler%20and%20ruled%20remain%20in%20a%20contract%20of%20trust%20in%20such%20purity%20of%20bonds%2C%20no%20tin-horn%20dictator%20may%20ever%20hope%20to%20subvert%20a%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20alas%2C%20when%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98bonds%E2%80%99%20becomes%20a%20dirty%2C%20clandestine%2C%20suspiciously%20underhand%20and%20transactional%20link%20between%20the%20extorting%20power%20broker%20and%20the%20Mammonite%20wealth%20accumulator%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20trust%20which%20democracy%20depends%20on%20stands%20betrayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20bonds%20that%20must%20exist%20between%20governed%20and%20governor%2C%20chosen%20by%20the%20citizen%2C%20come%20to%20terminal%20grief%2C%20letting%20loose%20a%20reign%20of%20falsehood%2C%20chicanery%2C%20subversions%20of%20law%20and%20ethics%2C%20and%20also%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20street%2C%C2%A0%20on%20television%20screens%2C%20even%20within%20assemblies%20and%20parliaments.%20This%20is%20what%20helps%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20false%20prophets%20to%20take%20over%20the%20realm%20on%20the%20back%20of%20sectarian%20invocations%20of%20faith%20and%20imprecations%20against%20manufactured%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20perfectly%20upright%20citizens%20begin%20to%20speak%20edgewise%2C%20fearing%20the%20wrath%20of%20pugilists%20and%20impersonators%20who%20claim%20to%20speak%20for%20the%20fallen%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20safe-keep%2C%20brother%20strikes%20at%20brother%2C%20old%20acquaintances%20turn%20their%20faces%20away%2C%20books%20that%20ought%20to%20be%20read%20disappear%2C%20all%20bonds%20crushed%2C%20only%20the%20bond%20between%20the%20strong%20men%20and%20the%20giver%20of%20the%20dirty%20bond%20comes%20to%20rule%3B%20and%20a%20frightened%20populace%2C%20robbed%20of%20reason%2C%20turn%20to%20sheep%2C%20regurgitating%20a%20common%2C%20uniform%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20Sanatan%2C%20Vishwa%20Guru%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20bonds%20may%20be%20anonymous%2C%20but%20there%20is%20real%20lucre%20in%20them.%20The%20ministers%20who%20designed%20this%20crooked%20scheme%20are%20trying%20to%20play%20down%20the%20malignancy.%20How%20deep%20the%20the%20cancer%20has%20spread%20will%20be%20known%20on%20June%204%2C%20when%20the%20results%20of%20the%20election%20are%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBadri%20Raina%20is%20a%20well-known%20commentator%20on%20politics%2C%20culture%20and%20society.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20hre