.com%2F2024%2F03%2F20%2Flifestyle%2Fman-put-in-coma-with-4-survival-chance-thanks-to-ingrown-groin-hair%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESilent%20Killer%20Takes%20Hold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESepsis%20is%20a%20serious%20medical%20emergency%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsilent%20killer%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20diagnose.%20The%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%20estimates%20that%201.7%20million%20Americans%20develop%20sepsis%20each%20year%2C%20with%20nearly%20270%2C000%20deaths%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Steven's%20case%2C%20the%20infection%20caused%20by%20the%20ingrown%20hair%20escalated%20into%20septic%20shock%2C%20leading%20to%20blood%20clots%2C%20pneumonia%2C%20organ%20failure%2C%20and%20acute%20respiratory%20distress%20syndrome%20(ARDS).%20The%20infection%20even%20reached%20his%20heart%2C%20causing%20significant%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20%5Bthe%20doctors%5D%20could%20figure%20out%20was%20that%20he%20was%20bleeding%20internally%20from%20somewhere.%20Little%20did%20we%20know%20that%20would%20be%20the%20smallest%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20sister%20Michelle%20wrote%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhelp-steven-fight-for-his-life%5C%22%3EGoFundMe%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20raised%20more%20than%20%248%2C000%20for%20his%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20declined%20fast%20until%20he%20crashed%20and%20was%20put%20on%20life%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20caught%20a%20rare%20bacteria%20that%20was%20ravaging%20%5Bthrough%5D%20his%20body%20and%20shutting%20down%20all%20his%20organs.%20He%20is%20severely%20septic%20and%20in%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoctors%20battled%20for%20survival%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20critical%20nature%20of%20his%20condition%2C%20Steven%20was%20placed%20in%20a%20medically%20induced%20coma%20to%20allow%20his%20body%20to%20heal.%20Doctors%20initially%20declared%20him%20brain%20dead%20and%20gave%20him%20a%20very%20low%20chance%20of%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20a%20month%20of%20intensive%20treatments%20and%20procedures%2C%20Steven%20defied%20the%20odds.%20He%20emerged%20from%20the%20coma%20with%20no%20brain%20damage%20and%20has%20since%20made%20a%20near-full%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710997980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F2f58v79o_coma_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fingrown-groyne-hair-leaves-us-man-in-coma-with-4-chance-of-survival-5280648%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Steven%20Spinale%20developed%20the%20condition%20as%20a%20result%20of%20an%20infection%20he%20contracted%20while%20attempting%20to%20remove%20the%20ingrown%20hair%20from%20his%20groin%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fingrown-groyne-hair-leaves-us-man-in-coma-with-4-chance-of-survival-5280648%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fingrown-groyne-hair-leaves-us-man-in-coma-with-4-chance-of-survival-5280648%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fingrown-groyne-hair-leaves-us-man-in-coma-with-4-chance-of-survival-5280648%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20of%20survivors%20of%20Pearl%20Harbor%20attack%20dies%20at%20102%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710997880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108666670%2Cimgsize-646941.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2F1-of-survivors-of-pearl-harbor-attack-dies-at-102%2Farticleshow%2F108666466.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi