wp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%2020)%20criticised%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20keeping%20people%20in%20jail%20endlessly%20before%20trial%2C%20and%20filing%20supplementary%20chargesheets%20so%20that%20the%20accused%20cannot%20avail%20the%20default%20bail%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fed-cannot-keep-persons-jail-indefinitely-without-trial-supreme-court%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20court%20was%20bothered%20by%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20practice%20of%20keeping%20trials%20going%20indefinitely%20while%20keeping%20the%20accused%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20object%20of%20default%20bail%20is%20that%20you%20do%20not%20arrest%20until%20investigation%20is%20complete.%20You%20cannot%20say%20trial%20will%20not%20commence%20unless%20investigation%20is%20not%20complete.%20You%20cannot%20keep%20on%20filing%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20and%20the%20person%20is%20in%20jail%20without%20trial.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20person%20is%20behind%20bars%20for%2018%20months.%20This%20is%20bothering%20us.%20In%20some%20case%20we%20will%20take%20it%20up%20and%20we%20are%20putting%20you%20to%20notice%20in%20that.%20Trial%20has%20to%20be%20begin%20when%20you%20arrest%20an%20accused%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%20to%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20who%20was%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20default%20bail%20plea%20filed%20by%20former%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20associate%20Prem%20Prakash%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20August%202022.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20denied%20Prakash%20bail%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20court%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20judges%20noted%20that%20Prakash%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20for%2018%20months%20and%20it%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20bail.%20The%20courtroom%20exchange%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20went%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20bail%20Mr%20Raju.%20Is%20it%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20interesting%20questions%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20ASG%20Raju%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInteresting%20okay%20but%20the%20person%20is%20behind%20bars%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20evidence%20tampering%2C%E2%80%9D%20ASG%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20come%20to%20us%20if%20he%20does%20any%20of%20that.%20But%2018%20months%20in%20jail%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710996731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-criticised-eds-practice-of-keeping-accused-imprisoned-endlessly-without-trial%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTrial%20has%20to%20be%20begin%20when%20you%20arrest%20an%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-criticised-eds-practice-of-keeping-accused-imprisoned-endlessly-without-trial%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Challenges%209th%20Probe%20Agency%20Summons%20In%20Delhi%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20moved%20a%20fresh%20plea%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20seeking%20no%20coercive%20action%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Excise%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Division%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20this%20morning.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20issued%209%20summons%20to%20him%20in%20the%20Excise%20case%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20during%20the%20hearing%20in%20the%20related%20matter%20before%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20his%20lawyers%20stated%20that%20they%20have%20apprehension%20that%20ED%20will%20arrest%20him%20and%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20appear%20if%20he%20is%20given%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED's%20last%20summon%20in%20the%20Excise%20Case%2C%20the%20financial%20probe%20agency%20has%20called%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20March%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20sought%20the%20response%20of%20the%20ED%20on%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20challenging%20the%20summons%20issued%20to%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20bench%20asked%20the%20Kejriwal%20lawyers%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20you%20appear%20before%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20reply%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20said%20that%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20were%20also%20arrested%20by%20the%20agency.%20We%20have%20an%20apprehension%20that%20ED%20will%20arrest%20him%2C%20but%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20appear%20if%20he%20is%20given%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20through%20plea%20has%20sought%2C%20the%20declaration%20of%20section%20(2)%20(s)%20of%20PMLA%20to%20be%20ultra%20vires%2C%20unconstitutional%20and%20arbitrary%20insofar%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20is%20construed%20to%20include%20a%20political%20party%20within%20its%20ambit%20and%20sweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20plea%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20present%20petition%20is%20being%20filed%20in%20extremely%20urgent%20and%20emergent%20circumstances%20where%20such%20arbitrary%20procedure%20under%20PMLA%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20employed%20to%20create%20a%20non-level%20playing%20field%20for%20the%20impending%20general%20elections%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20from%20April%2019%2C%202024%2C%20and%20to%20skew%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%20that%20controls%20the%20ED%20through%20Ministry%20of%20Finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20said%20action%20is%20being%20taken%20given%20Petitioner's%20role%20as%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20his%20role%20as%20an%20opposition%20leader%20and%20partner%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20contesting%20the%20General%20Election%20to%20be%20held%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20use%20of%20such%20provisions%20of%20PMLA%20for%20investigation%2Farrest%20or%20threat%20thereof%2C%20ED%20being%20in%20control%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%20has%20been%20weaponized%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20coerce%20a%20change%20in%20the%20political%20landscape%20of%20the%20country%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%2C%26quot%3B%20Kejriwal%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20further%20stated%20that%20it%20is%20the%20case%20of%20Petitioner%20that%20the%20said%20impugned%20summons%20dated%20February%2026%2C%202024%2C%20and%20March%2016%2C%202024%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Petitioner%20with%20an%20oblique%20motive%20to%20arrest%20the%20Petitioner%20(Kejriwal).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20in%20the%20present%20matter%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%20August%2022%2C%202022%2C%20i.e.%2C%20for%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20and%20after%20investigation-%20as%20many%20as%206%20Prosecution%20Complaints%20with%20thousands%20of%20documents%20stand%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20necessary%20documents%2F%20information%20are%20already%20in%20possession%20of%20Respondent%20and%20summoning%20Petitioner%20%26quot%3Bin%20person%26quot%3B%20is%20therefore%20a%20ploy%20to%20illegally%20arrest%20Petitioner%20and%20the%20present%20matter%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20malice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20elaborate%20complaints%20with%20thousands%20of%20documents%20are%20filed%20by%20the%20Respondent-%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20all%20relevant%20material%20and%20information%20is%20already%20in%20possession%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Additional%20Chief%20Metropolitan%20Magistrate%20of%20Rouse%20Avenue%20Court%20granted%20bail%20to%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20two%20complaints%20filed%20by%20ED%20for%20non-compliance%20with%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20agency.%20During%20the%20hearing%2C%20Kejriwal%20appeared%20physically%20before%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20agency%20wants%20to%20record%20Kejriwal's%20statement%20in%20the%20case%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20formulation%20of%20policy%2C%20meetings%20held%20before%20it%20was%20finalized%2C%20and%20allegations%20of%20bribery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20sixth%20charge%20sheet%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20on%20December%202%2C%202023%2C%20naming%20AAP%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20his%20aide%20Sarvesh%20Mishra%2C%20the%20ED%20claimed%20that%20the%20AAP%20used%20kickbacks%20worth%20Rs%2045%20crore%20generated%20via%20the%20policy%20as%20part%20of%20its%20assembly%20elections%20campaign%20in%20Goa%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20now-scrapped%20excise%20policy%20was%20aimed%20%26quot%3Bat%20revitalizing%20the%20city's%20flagging%20liquor%20business%26quot%3B%20and%20replacing%20a%20sales-volume-based%20regime%20with%20a%20licence%20fee%20for%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20Governor%20Vinai%20Kumar%20Saxena%20had%20ordered%20a%20probe%20into%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20policy.%20AAP%20has%20accused%20Saxena's%20predecessor%2C%20Anil%20Baijal%2C%20of%20sabotaging%20the%20move%20with%20a%20few%20last-minute%20changes%20that%20resulted%20in%20lower-than-expected%20revenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20senior%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20are%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20case.%20Sisodia%2C%20who%20was%20the%20then%20Delhi%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20February%2026%20following%20several%20rounds%20of%20questioning.%20On%20October%205%2C%20ED%20arrested%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710996720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc3gh0c4g_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-challenges-9th-probe-agency-summons-in-delhi-high-court-5280222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20moved%20a%20fresh%20plea%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20seeking%20no%20coercive%20action%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Excise%20policy%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-challenges-9th-probe-agency-summons-in-delhi-high-court-5280222%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-challenges-9th-probe-agency-summons-in-delhi-high-court-5280222%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-challenges-9th-probe-agency-summons-in-delhi-high-court-5280222%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Misleading%20ads%3A%20Patanjali%20submits%20apology%20to%20SC%22%2C%22content%2