rmers-congress-promises-right-to-msp-if-india-bloc-comes-to-power-aap-tmc-slam-bjp%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eegalising%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20other%20guarantees%20include%20assurances%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frozgaar-revolution-congress-promises-rs-5000-cr-startup-fund-govt-jobs-safety-net-for-gig-work%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eright%20to%20apprenticeship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20end%20to%20paper%20leaks%2C%20filling%20vacant%20posts%20for%20government%20jobs%2C%20commitment%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ejal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20jungle%2C%20%3Cem%3Ezameen%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20under%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fadivasi-nyay-as-congress-announces-five-guarantees-bjp-keeps-special-focus-on-tribal-welfare%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAdivasi%20sankalp%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20Hissedari%20Nyay%20bracket%2C%20and%20guarantees%20for%20women%20including%2050%25%20reservation%20for%20them%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20and%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20year%20to%20every%20woman%20belonging%20to%20poor%20households%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20days%20after%20the%20end%20of%20Yatra%2C%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20meeting%20discussed%20these%20guarantees%20and%20said%20that%20these%20would%20foreground%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%20polls%2C%20which%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20CWC%20meeting%2C%20Kharge%20congratulated%20Gandhi%20on%20his%20two%20yatras%20and%20said%20that%20they%20were%20not%20just%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%E2%80%9D%20marches%2C%20but%20the%20largest%20%E2%80%9Cmass%20contact%20movement%20in%20our%20political%20history%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20the%20manifesto%20itself%2C%20which%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Kharge%20for%20his%20authorisation%2C%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20document%20but%20roadmaps%20based%20on%20dialogue%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20party%20will%20fight%20the%20elections%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20these%20five%20Nyay%20resolutions%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20will%20touch%20every%20Indian%E2%80%99s%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EElectoral%20impact%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20guarantees%20now%20being%20pushed%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20its%20electoral%20impact%20remains%20under%20question%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20its%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20job%20of%20a%20political%20party%20is%20to%20win%20elections%2C%20the%20job%20of%20political%20leaders%20is%20to%20increase%20the%20vote%20share.%20The%20problem%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%20both%20its%20phases%20is%20that%20it%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20increase%20the%20vote%20share%20substantially%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahseed%20Kidwai%2C%20visiting%20fellow%20at%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20and%20political%20commentator%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20the%20Congress%20won%2044%20seats%20with%2019.3%25%20vote%20share.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20it%20first%20brought%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fcongress-nyay-minimum-income-elections-2019%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eidea%20of%20Nyay%20in%20its%20manifesto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20bettered%20its%20tally%20to%2052%20seats%20but%20its%20vote%20share%20remained%20at%2019.5%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20objective%C2%A0%20of%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%20both%20phases%20would%20be%20to%20support%20the%20vote%20percentage%20from%2019%25%20to%20somewhere%20around%2025%25%20which%20would%20have%20given%20it%20political%20strength%20in%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kidwai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20we%20have%20seen%20is%20that%20in%20the%20assembly%202023%20elections%20it%20did%20not%20lead%20to%20substantial%20increase%20in%20vote%20share.%20So%20the%20promises%20they%20have%20made%2C%20need%20to%20be%20assessed%20how%20much%20impact%20it%20is%20making%20electorally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Yatra%20has%20been%20questioned%2C%20with%20precious%20political%20time%20being%20lost%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20focusing%20on%20the%20polls%20and%20alliance%20building%20had%20come%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt%2C%20and%20then%20the%20Yatra%20which%20saw%20its%20fallout%20with%20the%20alliance%20unravelling%2C%20the%20challenge%20remains%20in%20direct%20contests%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20at%20least%20200-odd%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-has-no-option-but-to-recover-in-heartland-states-in-2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enorth%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20down%20to%20a%20straight%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Congress%20becomes%20closer%20to%20100%20seats%2C%20there%20is%20a%20reduction%20in%20BJP%20seats.%20Its%20allies%20are%20capable%20%E2%80%93%20the%20RJD%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%2C%20and%20even%20Samajwadi%20Party%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20and%20take%20some%20seats.%20But%20it%20is%20the%20direct%20contests%20where%20Congress%E2%80%99%20strike%20rate%20is%20poor%20and%20that%20poses%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kidwai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710995289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21095727%2FGIxupJLW0AAqetg.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-electoral-impact%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20its%20symbolic%20start%20in%20Manipur%2C%20much%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20the%20stream%20of%20Indian%20politics%20for%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20as%20questions%20linger%20on%20the%20very%20strategy%20that%20led%20the%20party%20to%20launch%20the%20yatra%20in%20the%20first%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-electoral-impact%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yeh%20Rishta's%20Charu%20aka%20Saloni%20Sandhu%20on%20her%20bond%20with%20co-stars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710995257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108665438%2Cimgsize-1443310.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fexclusive-yeh-rishtas-charu-aka-saloni-sandhu-on-her-bond-with-co-stars-says-i-shared-a-strong-bond-with-pratiksha-honmukhe%2Farticleshow%2F108665246.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajan%20Shahi%20replaced%20Shehzada%20Dhami%20and%20Pratiksha%20Honmukhe%20with%20Rohit%20Purohit%20and%20Garvita%20Sadhwani%20on%20'Yeh%20Rishta%20Kya%20Kehlata%20Hai'.%20Charu%20(Saloni%20Sandhu)%20enjoys%20her%20role%2C%20appreciates%20the%20legacy%2C%20and%20values%20relationships%20on%20set.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20Saloni%20had%20to%20say%20about%20working%20with%20former%20Ruhi%20aka%20Pratiksha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SHRUTI%20SAMPAT%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fexclusive-yeh-rishtas-charu-aka-saloni-sandhu-on-her-bond-with-co-stars-says-i-shared-a-st