00068_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-on-march-21-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-rvnl-124032100068_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-on-march-21-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-rvnl-124032100068_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indonesia's%20Prabowo%20confirmed%20as%20next%20president%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710993838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FC27B%2Fproduction%2F_132978794_98b6e429d3614ecf12e9ba8b45d4ffbc65a4aa110_0_2558_17061000x667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68622796%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20general%20says%20'give%20us%20a%20chance'%20as%20his%20rivals%20vow%20to%20contest%20the%20election%20result.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68622796%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68622796.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68622796.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Patanjali's%20Apology%20Day%20After%20Supreme%20Court%20Summons%20Ramdev%20In%20Ads%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAcharya%20Balkrishna%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20and%20an%20aide%20of%20Yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%2C%20has%20apologised%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20the%20company's%20misleading%20claims%20about%20its%20products%20and%20their%20medicinal%20efficacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20was%20filed%20yesterday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20for%20not%20responding%20to%20a%20contempt%20notice%20over%20misleading%20advertisements.%20The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20had%20asked%20Balkrishna%20and%20Ramdev%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20on%20April%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20in%20the%20court%2C%20Mr%20Balkrishna%20has%20said%20he%20has%20the%20highest%20regards%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20Extending%20an%20%26quot%3Bunqualified%20apology%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20the%20company%20will%20%26quot%3Bensure%20that%20such%20advertisements%20are%20not%20issued%20in%20the%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Balkrishna%20clarified%20that%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bintention%20is%20only%20to%20exhort%20the%20citizens%20of%20this%20country%20to%20lead%20a%20healthier%20life%20by%20consuming%20products%26quot%3B%20of%20Patanjali%2C%20including%20those%20%26quot%3Bfor%20lifestyle%20ailments%20through%20the%20use%20age%20old%20literature%20and%20materials%20supplementing%20and%20backed%20by%20ayurvedic%20research%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20provisions%20of%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Magic%20Remedies%20(Objectionable%20Advertisements)%20Act%2C%20which%20prohibits%20advertisements%20of%20magic%20cure%20claims%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Barchaic%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20last%20changes%20in%20the%20legislation%20were%20made%20when%20%26quot%3Bscientific%20evidence%20in%20Ayurveda%20research%20were%20lacking%26quot%3B.%20Patanjali%2C%20the%20affidavit%20said%2C%20now%20has%20%26quot%3Bevidence-based%20scientific%20data%20with%20clinical%20research%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Econducted%20in%20Ayurveda%2C%20which%20would%20demonstrate%20the%20advances%20made%20through%20scientific%20research%20in%20the%20context%20of%20diseases%20mentioned%20in%20the%20said%20schedule%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20same%20it%20is%20humbly%20submitted%20that%20the%20Deponent's%20only%20quest%20is%20for%20a%20better%20and%20healthier%20life%20for%20each%20and%20every%20citizen%20and%20to%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20the%20countries%20healthcare%20infrastructure%20by%20providing%20holistic%2C%20evidence%20based%20solutions%20for%20lifestyle%20related%20medical%20complications%20through%20the%20usage%20of%20age%20old%20traditional%20approach%20of%20Ayurveda%20and%20Yoga%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202006%20by%20Mr%20Ramdev%20and%20Mr%20Balkrishna%2C%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20is%20a%20multinational%20conglomerate%20that%20manufactures%20a%20long%20list%20of%20products%2C%20ranging%20from%20ayurvedic%20medicine%20to%20cosmetics%20to%20food%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conglomerate%20has%20run%20into%20trouble%20over%20misleading%20advertisements%20about%20the%20efficacy%20of%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Patanjali%2C%20citing%20its%20failure%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20notice%20for%20contempt%20proceedings.%20The%20court%20directed%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20to%20appear%20before%20it.%20It%20also%20noted%20that%20Patanjali%20Ayurved's%20advertisements%20were%20in%20the%20teeth%20of%20an%20undertaking%20given%20to%20the%20court%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2021%20last%20year%2C%20Patanjali's%20counsel%20had%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20%26quot%3Bhenceforth%20there%20shall%20not%20be%20any%20violation%20of%20any%20law(s)%2C%20especially%20relating%20to%20advertising%20or%20branding%20of%20products%20manufactured%20and%20marketed%20by%20it%20and%2C%20further%2C%20that%20no%20casual%20statements%20claiming%20medicinal%20efficacy%20or%20against%20any%20system%20of%20medicine%20will%20be%20released%20to%20the%20media%20in%20any%20form%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20that%20alleged%20a%20smear%20campaign%20by%20Ramdev%20against%20the%20Covid%20vaccination%20drive%20and%20modern%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710993660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Fje5130c_ramdev-patanjali-reuters_625x300_12_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpatanjali-acharya-balkrishna-supreme-court-intention-only-to-patanjalis-apology-to-supreme-court-in-ads-case-5280295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Acharya%20Balkrishna%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20and%20an%20aide%20of%20Yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%2C%20has%20apologised%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20the%20company's%20misleading%20claims%20about%20its%20products%20and%20their%20medicinal%20efficacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpatanjali-acharya-balkrishna-supreme-court-intention-only-to-patanjalis-apology-to-supreme-court-in-ads-case-5280295%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpatanjali-acharya-balkrishna-supreme-court-intention-only-to-patanjalis-apology-to-supreme-court-in-ads-case-5280295%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpatanjali-acharya-balkrishna-supreme-court-intention-only-to-patanjalis-apology-to-supreme-court-in-ads-case-5280295%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italy%20PM%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20Seeks%20Over%20%24100%2C000%20In%20Damages%20Over%20Deepfake%20Videos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EItaly's%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20is%20seeking%20100%2C000%20euros%20(%24109%2C345)%20in%20damages%20after%20deepfake%20porn%20videos%20of%20her%20were%20created%20and%20circulated%20online.%20Investigators%20claim%20that%20the%20two%20men%20made%20pornographic%20videos%20of%20Ms%20Meloni%20by%20superimposing%20her%20face%20on%20another%20person's%20body%20and%20then%20uploaded%20them%20on%20the%20internet.%20The%2040-year-old%20man%20and%20his%2073-year-old%20father%20are%20charged%20with%20defamation%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68615474%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20locate%20them%20by%20tracking%20the%20smartphone%20that%20was%20used%20to%20upload%20the%20videos.%20The%20deepfake%20video%20in%20question%20dates%20back%20to%202022%2C%20before%20she%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20country's%20Prime%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20certain%20defamation%20cases%20in%20Italy%20may%20be%20criminal%20and%20result%20in%20a%20jail%20sentence.%20Ms%20Meloni%20will%20testify%20before%20a%20court%20on%202%20July.%20The%20indictment%20claims%20that%20the%20videos%20were%20uploaded%20on%20a%20pornographic%20website%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20watched%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20of%20times%26quot%3B%20over%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20team%20of%20the%20Italian%20PM%20said%20that%20the%20request%20for%20damages%20was%20%26quot%3Bsymbolic%26quot%3B.%20They%20added%20that%20Ms%20Meloni%20would%20donate%20the%20entire%20amount%20to%20%26quot%3Bsupport%20women%20who%20have%20been%20victims%20of%20male%20violence.%26quot%3B%20Maria%20Giulia%20Marongiu%2C%20Ms%20Meloni's%20lawyer%2C%20said%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20compensation%20will%20%26quot%3Bsend%20a%20message%20to%20women%20who%20are%20victims%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20abuse%20of%20power%20not%20to%20be%20afraid%20to%20press%20charges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deepfake%20is%20a%20type%20of%20synthetic%20media%20that%20uses%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20manipulate%20or%20generate%20visual%20and%20audio%20content%2C%20often%20with%20a%20malicious%20motive%2C%20to%20appear%20authentic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%26quot%3Bdeepfake%26quot%3B%20originally%20appeared%20in%20late%202017%2C%20according%20to%20MIT%2C%20when%20a%20user%20of%20the%20same%20name%20on%20Reddit%20established%20a%20platform%20for%20sharing%20pornographic%20videos%20made%20with%20open-source%20face-swapping%20technology.%20With%20deepfake%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20is%20used%20to%20create%20photos%20or%20movies%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20fake%20occurrences.%20It%20uses%20a%20form%20of%20AI%20called%20deep%20learning%20to%20make%20images%20or%20videos%20of%20fake%20events.%20Deepfakes%20have%20become%20more%20realistic%20and%20commonplace%20due%20to%20advancements%20in%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20become%20a%20danger%20to%20public%20confidence%20and%20the%20truth.%20Deepfakes%20are%20a%20powerful%20tool%20for%20spreading%20misinformation%2C%20twisting%20public%20opinion%2C%20and%20damaging%20reputations%20because%20they%20can%20be%20used%20to%20create%20convincing%20audio%20and%20video%20recordings%20of%20individuals%20saying%20or%20doing%20things%20they%20never%20did.%20Many%20world%20leaders%20have%20expressed%20their%20concern%20about%20the%20growing%20nature%20of%20deepfakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710993540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ft24jgljg_italy-pm-giorgia-meloni_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fitaly-pm-giorgia-meloni-seeks-over-100-000-in-damages-over-deepfake-videos-5280348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20indictment%20claims%20that%20the%20videos%20were%20uploaded%20on%20a%20pornographic%20website%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20watched%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20of%20times%26quot%3B%20over%20several%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fitaly-pm-giorgia-meloni-seeks-over-100-000-in-damages-over-deepfake-videos-5280348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fitaly-pm-giorgia-meloni-seeks-over-100-000-in-damages-over-deepfake-videos-5280348%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%