%20Sidhu%20named%20the%20batter%20he%20rates%20the%20highest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pre-IPL%20chat%2C%20Sidhu%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20feels%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20bat%20at%20the%20No.%203%20spot%20for%20the%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore.%20Sidhu%20wasn't%20in%20agreement%20with%20the%20idea%2C%20though%20he%20admitted%20that%20he%20is%20the%20greatest%20batter%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20so.%20It's%20what%20the%20team%20demands.%20You%20could%20be%20the%20greatest%20player%20in%20the%20world%2C%20which%20he%20is.%20But%20if%20your%20team%20is%20not%20winning%2C%20especially%20hasn't%20held%20the%20trophy%20once%2C%20then%20it's%20a%20blot%20that%20you%20would%20want%20to%20erase.%20It's%20not%20detrimental%20to%20him%20in%20anyway%2C%20because%20he%20has%20given%20his%20best%20and%20you%20could%20see%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20rated%20him%20as%20the%20best%20Indian%20batter%20ever.%20There%20are%20eras%20where%20I%20would%20put%20up%20my%20transistor%20and%20listen%20to%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20bat%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20those%20are%20the%2070s.%20The%20great%20West%20Indies%20fast%20bowlers%2C%20bunking%20school%20and%20just%20going%20out%20one%20period%20and%20listening%20to%20how%20he%20was%20batting%20and%20without%20a%20helmet%2C%20that%20was%20his%20era.%20He%20dominated%20for%20almost%2015-20%20years.%20Then%20came%20Tendulkar%2C%20another%20era.%20Then%20came%20Dhoni%2C%20and%20then%20came%20Virat.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20four%2C%20I%20would%20rate%20him%20as%20the%20best%20because%20he%20has%20adapted%20to%20all%20three%20formats%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20same%20way%2C%20his%20technical%20ability%20and%20the%20fittest%20of%20all%20of%20them.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20all%20four%2C%20he%20would%20be%20the%20fittest.%20Tendulkar%20had%20problems%2C%20in%20the%20latter%20stages%20of%20his%20career.%20Dhoni%2C%20he%20is%20fit.%20Virat%20is%20super%20fit.%20That%20holds%20him%20in%20good%20stead.%20It%20elevates%20him%20to%20a%20level%2C%20a%20few%20notches%20higher%2C%20that%20others%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20achieve.%20The%20longevity%20factor%2C%20gives%20him%20a%20plus.%20The%20adaptability%20factor%20is%20Sone%20Pe%20Suhaaga%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20the%20former%20India%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710989160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3745mq7_navjot-singh-sidhu_640x480_19_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Frated-him-best-indian-batter-ever-navjot-sidhus-dhoni-vs-kohli-vs-sachin-vs-gavaskar-verdict-5273404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20cricketer%20Navjot%20Singh%20Sidhu%20picked%20the%20best%20Indian%20batter%20ever%20from%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20and%20Sunil%20Gavaskar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reddit%20Hits%20%246.4%20Billion%20Valuation%20Ahead%20Of%20Wall%20Street%20Debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Reddit%20social%20network%20was%20set%20to%20make%20its%20trading%20debut%20Thursday%20after%20pricing%20robustly%20in%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%20that%20suggested%20greater%20investor%20enthusiasm%20for%20new%20stock%20issuers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddit%20is%20set%20to%20debut%20Thursday%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20under%20the%20ticker%20RDDT%20after%20an%20IPO%20priced%20at%20%2434%20dollars%20a%20share%2C%20the%20company%20said%20Wednesday%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20which%20would%20value%20the%20platform%20at%20around%20%246.4%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entry%20of%20Reddit%20comes%20as%20the%20tech%20sector%20is%20seeing%20a%20big%20slowdown%20in%20IPOs%20since%20the%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20started%20hiking%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20easy%20financing%20scarce%2C%20Silicon%20Valley%20is%20seeing%20a%20dearth%20of%20companies%20ready%20to%20make%20the%20big%20leap%20to%20go%20public%2C%20with%20Pinterest%20being%20the%20last%20social%20media%20company%20to%20do%20so%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco-based%20Reddit%20first%20filed%20for%20its%20IPO%20in%202021%20when%20the%20market%20was%20hot%20thanks%20to%20a%20Covid-linked%20growth%20boom%20for%20tech%2C%20but%20the%20attempt%20stalled%20as%20the%20internet%20economy%20cooled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddit%20--%20unlike%20Facebook%20or%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20--%20is%20siloed%20into%20about%20100%2C000%20subject-focused%20chatrooms%20known%20as%20subreddits%2C%20making%20it%20more%20specialized%20and%20a%20place%20where%20posts%20are%20less%20prone%20to%20going%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20Reddit%20has%2073%20million%20average%20daily%20users%20and%20267%20million%20monthly%20users%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20according%20to%20its%20filing%20to%20US%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContent%20in%20subreddits%20is%20mostly%20moderated%20independently%2C%20with%20the%20site%20demanding%20a%20basic%20standard%20that%20users%20must%20adhere%20to%2C%20making%20it%20less%20policed%20or%20centralized%20than%20Facebook%20or%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20filing%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20company%20said%20that%20it%20would%20issue%2015.2%20million%20shares%20priced%20between%20%2431%20and%20%2434.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20lead%20of%20companies%20like%20Airbnb%20and%20Rivian%2C%20Reddit%20set%20aside%20about%20eight%20percent%20of%20the%20IPO%20shares%20for%20moderators%20and%20top%20users%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BRedditors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EFuture%20profits%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20on%20whether%20Reddit%20will%20be%20a%20successful%20business%20and%20the%20company%20has%20never%20turned%20a%20profit%20in%20its%20two%20decades%20of%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20faithful%20yet%20often%20unruly%20users%2C%20Reddit%20is%20not%20seen%20as%20fertile%20ground%20to%20grow%20advertising%2C%20which%20will%20be%20the%20main%20path%20for%20the%20company%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddit%20was%20created%20in%202005%20and%20was%20quickly%20sold%20to%20Conde%20Nast%2C%20the%20publisher%20of%20Vogue%20and%20the%20New%20Yorker%20magazine%2C%20in%20an%20unlikely%20pairing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Reddit%20was%20spun-off%2C%20though%20Conde%20Nast's%20parent%20company%2C%20controlled%20by%20the%20Newhouse%20family%2C%20remains%20the%20biggest%20shareholder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20is%20also%20a%20major%20investor%20after%20he%20led%20a%20fundraising%20round%20about%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710987900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7v2fn1ao_reddit-generic_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsocial-media-firm-reddit-hits-6-4-billion-valuation-ahead-of-wall-street-debut-5280009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reddit%20social%20network%20was%20set%20to%20make%20its%20trading%20debut%20Thursday%20after%20pricing%20robustly%20in%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%20that%20suggested%20greater%20investor%20enthusiasm%20for%20new%20stock%20issuers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsocial-media-firm-reddit-hits-6-4-billion-valuation-ahead-of-wall-street-debut-5280009