%20were%20contaminated%20with%20the%20potent%20carcinogen%20benzene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Acne%20%26amp%3B%20Rosacea%20Society%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20storing%20benzoyl%20peroxide%20creams%2C%20gels%20and%20washes%20at%20refrigerated%20temperatures%20could%20minimize%20the%20risk%20of%20benzene%20exposure.%20%26quot%3BBenzoyl%20peroxide%20has%20been%20a%20very%20important%20part%20of%20the%20treatment%20of%20many%20patients%20with%20acne%20and%20also%20some%20other%20skin%20diseases%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20group%2C%20which%20has%20about%206%2C000%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20testing%20lab%20Valisure%20filed%20a%20petition%20with%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20on%20March%205%20asking%20the%20agency%20to%20recall%20benzoyl%20peroxide%20acne%20treatments%20after%20finding%20high%20levels%20of%20benzene%20in%20the%20products%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20has%20reported.%20Benzene%20levels%20increased%20when%20products%20underwent%20stability%20testing%2C%20including%20Proactiv's%202.5%25%20benzoyl%20peroxide%20cream%2C%20manufactured%20by%20Taro%20Pharmaceutical%20Industries%20Ltd.%2C%20and%2010%25%20benzoyl%20peroxide%20cream%20from%20Reckitt%20Benckiser%20Group%20Plc's%20Clearasil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20given%20benzoyl%20peroxide%20has%20been%20used%20for%20five%20decades%2C%20AARS%20President%20James%20Del%20Rosso%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20group%20said%20more%20research%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20sure%20that%20any%20guidance%20that%20is%20given%20and%20any%20decisions%20that%20are%20made%20are%20based%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20on%20solid%20scientific%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20Del%20Rosso%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20has%20said%20it%20would%20work%20to%20verify%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20data%20Valisure%20presented%20in%20its%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20st