20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESeveral%20women%20told%20police%20they%20were%20all%20in%20good%20spirits%20during%20the%20get-together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFootage%20from%20cameras%20on%20the%20property%20showed%20Chao%20left%20the%20lodge%20and%20walked%20to%20her%20Tesla%20at%20around%2011%3A37%20p.m.%2C%20with%20a%20blanket%20wrapped%20around%20her%20and%20her%20cellphone%20held%20to%20her%20ear%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20A%20pond%20on%20the%20property%20was%20located%20between%20the%20guest%20house%20and%20the%20main%20house%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChao%2C%20in%20her%20Tesla%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangela-chao-foremost-group-death-tesla-gearshift-reverse-drowning-accident-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereversed%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20and%20over%20a%20limestone%20barrier%20wall%2C%20entering%20the%20water%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20Video%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efootage%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecameras%20on%20the%20property%20showed%20the%20Tesla%20then%20floated%20to%20the%20center%20of%20the%20pond%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20around%2011%3A42%20p.m.%2C%20Chao%20called%20one%20of%20the%20friends%20she%20had%20just%20had%20dinner%20with%2C%20Amber%20Landeau-Keinan%2C%20and%20calmly%20told%20her%20she%20was%20in%20the%20pond%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20After%20Chao%20said%20her%20feet%20were%20underwater%2C%20her%20friend%20told%20her%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20calm%20voice%2C%20Chao%20informs%20Keinan%20she%20is%20not%20able%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20report%20said%2C%20citing%20an%20interview%20with%20Landeau-Keinan.%20%26quot%3BChao%20told%20Keinan%20the%20water%20was%20rising%20and%20she%20was%20going%20to%20die%20and%20said%20'I%20love%20you'%20to%20Keinan%20prior%20to%20the%20vehicle%20going%20underwater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%20call%20lasted%20about%208%20minu