ain%20technology%20startup%20founded%20by%20Musk.%20Its%20implant%20allows%20a%20patient%20to%20use%20their%20thoughts%20to%20control%20a%20computer.%20Musk%20has%20said%20that%20the%20company%20will%20start%20by%20working%20with%20patients%20who%20have%20severe%20physical%20limitations%20like%20cervical%20spinal%20cord%20impairment%20or%20quadriplegia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20was%20streamed%20on%20Musk's%20social%20platform%20X%2C%20the%20patient%2C%20Noland%20Arbaugh%2C%20was%20able%20to%20use%20his%20computer%20to%20play%20chess%20and%20the%20game%20Civilization%20VI.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20given%20up%20on%20playing%20that%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20already%20changed%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Arbaugh%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20surgery%20was%20super%20easy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELivestream%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fneuralink%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Neuralink%3C%2Fa%3E%20demonstrating%20%E2%80%9CTelepathy%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20controlling%20a%20computer%20and%20playing%20video%20games%20just%20by%20thinking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0kHJdayfYy%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0kHJdayfYy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1770565942168420750%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArbaugh%2C%2029%2C%20said%20he%20sustained%20a%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bfreak%20diving%20accident%26quot%3B%20eight%20years%20ago.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20was%20released%20from%20the%20hospital%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Neuralink%20procedure%20in%20January%2C%20which%20went%20smoothly.%20He%20added%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bstill%20work%2