%20with%20Epic%20Games%20over%20app%20store%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20X%2C%20and%20Match%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.courtlistener.com%2Fdocket%2F17442392%2F904%2F1%2Fepic-games-inc-v-apple-inc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20brief%3C%2Fa%3E%20Wednesday%20that%20throws%20support%20behind%20Epic%20Games%20%E2%80%94%20the%20maker%20of%20Fortnite%20%E2%80%94%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-fortnite-epic-games-lawsuit-secrets-revealed-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edispute%20with%20Apple%20over%20in-app%20purchases%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-vs-epic-legal-battle-verdict-app-store-payments-business-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%202021%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20Apple%20wasn't%20complying%20with%20competition%20laws%20because%20it%20restricted%20developers%20from%20using%20payment%20processing%20services%20other%20than%20Apple's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20charges%20up%20to%2030%25%20fees%20for%20in-app%20purchases%20and%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20third-party%20developers%20to%20steer%20customers%20to%20alternative%20payment%20options%2C%20Fornite%20argued%20in%20its%20suit.%20A%20judge%20agreed%20and%20required%20Apple%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20model%20that%20would%20allow%20customers%20to%20use%20other%20payment%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20responded%20by%20allowing%20third-party%20developers%20to%20include%20a%20link%20that%20would%20lead%20users%20to%20an%20outside%20website%20for%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Meta%2C%20X%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Match%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20have%20developed%20major%20apps%20in%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20%E2%80%94%20said%20in%20their%20brief%20that%20Apple's%20solution%20doesn't%20do%20enough%20to%20give%20consumers%20payment%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple's%20new%20rest