n%3EWe%20used%20binoculars%20and%20a%20camera%20viewfinder%20to%20see%20animals%20that%20were%20further%20away.%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20our%20fair%20share%20of%20close-up%20sightings%2C%20but%20many%20of%20the%20animals%20we%20wanted%20to%20see%20were%20far%20away%20and%20sometimes%20not%20immediately%20obvious%20to%20the%20naked%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ditched%20our%20iPhones%20and%20used%20binoculars%20and%20someone's%20camera%20viewfinder%20to%20get%20a%20closer%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20pair%20of%20binoculars%20and%20a%20camera%20with%20a%20zoom%20lens%20are%20essential%20for%20getting%20the%20best%20view%20(and%20pictures)%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20were%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20with%20minimal%20animal%20sightings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20giraffes%20walk%20in%20a%20grassy%20area%20at%20sunset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65faeaee4af076d3cf91e811%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuring%20a%20safari%2C%20you%20can't%20control%20what%20animals%20you'll%20see%20or%20when%20you'll%20see%20them.%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESafari%20drives%20can%20be%20frustrating%20because%20you%20can't%20control%20what%20animals%20you'll%20see%2C%20how%20far%20away%20they%20are%2C%20and%20how%20long%20the%20sighting%20will%20last.%20But%20being%20patient%20can%20be%20rewarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20dusk%20drive%2C%20we%20spent%20three%20hours%20searching%20for%20a%20pride%20of%20lions%20without%20any%20luck.%20Finally%2C%20as%20the%20sun%20set%20in%20the%20last%20half%20hour%2C%20we%20stumbled%20upon%20three%20female%20lions%20napping%2C%20a%20leopard%2C%20and%20giraffes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20of%20the%20animals%20are%20sleeping%20during%20the%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expected%20to%20see%20animals%20moving%20around%20or%20hunting%2C%20but%20many%20were%20resting%20during%20the%20day.%20It%20was%20only%20when%20dusk%20approached%20that%20they%20started%20to%20slowly%20stake%20out%20a%20spot%20by%20the%20grazing%20herds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20go%20on%20safari%20again%2C%20I'll%20book%20a%20night%20drive%20so%20I%20can%20see%20how%20the%20lions%20and%20other%20animals%20act%20during%20their%20peak%20hours%20of%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20view%20was%20largely%20out%20of%20my%20control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Safari%20vehicles%20drive%20down%20a%20dirt%20road%2C%20with%20gazelles%20grazing%20in%20the%20grass%20on%20each%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65faeaee4af076d3cf91e813%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20often%20traffic%20jams%20along%20the%20safari%20route.%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20a%20less%20common%20animal%20like%20a%20lion%20or%20cheetah%20is%20spotted%2C%20a%20traffic%20jam%20of%20safari%20vehicles%20speed%20over%20and%20line%20up%2C%20vying%20for%20the%20best%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20you%20see%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%2C%20if%20you%20see%20anything%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20can%20depend%20on%20your%20driver%20and%20what%20vantage%20point%20they%20can%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20in%20safari%20vehicles%20hold%20up%20phones%20to%20take%20pictures%20of%20a%20giraffe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65faf0b74af076d3cf91eaf0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20moving%20around%20the%20car%20to%20get%20a%20better%20look%20at%20the%20animals.%20%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20view%