red%20Pannun%20a%20terrorist%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20public%20hearing%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%2020)%20of%20the%20US%20congressional%20committee%20on%20foreign%20affairs%20on%20the%20Pakistan%20elections%2C%20Democrat%20congressman%20from%20Minnesota%20Dean%20Phillips%20quizzed%20a%20senior%20state%20department%20official%20about%20the%20accusation%20made%20by%20US%20prosecutors%2C%20asking%20if%20the%20department%20has%20considered%20placing%20sanctions%20on%20Indian%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20administration%20of%20course%20recently%20placed%20sanctions%20on%20more%20than%20500%20individuals%20relating%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Alexei%20Navalny%20in%20Russia%20on%20Russian%20soil.%20So%20my%20question%20is%2C%20are%20any%20similar%20sanctions%20on%20or%20travel%20bans%20being%20considered%20for%20those%20who%20we%20believe%20may%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20attempted%20murder%20of%20Mr%20Pannun%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20asked%20Phillips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20state%20for%20South%20and%20Central%20Asia%2C%20Donald%20Lu%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20took%20the%20allegations%20%E2%80%9Cincredibly%20seriously%20and%20have%20raised%20it%20at%20the%20highest%20levels%20with%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20at%20the%20moment%20working%20with%20India%20to%20encourage%20India%20to%20hold%20accountable%20those%20responsible%20for%20this%20this%20terrible%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lu%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20India%20has%20announced%20a%20committee%20of%20inquiry%2C%20Lu%20declared%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20ask%20them%20to%20work%20quickly%20and%20transparently%20to%20make%20sure%20justice%20is%20done%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELu%20didn%E2%80%99t%20indicate%20with%20his%20remarks%20that%20India%20had%20conveyed%20any%20findings%20from%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20November%20indictment%2C%20US%20prosecutors%20named%20the%20Indian%20official%20accused%20of%20recruiting%20Gupta%20only%20as%20%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99%20but%20said%20his%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20the%20US%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20is%20also%20said%20to%20have%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csenior%20field%20officer%E2%80%9D%20with%20responsibilities%20in%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20management%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cintelligence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20says%20the%20alleged%20murder%20plot%20was%20thwarted%20by%20US%20law%20enforcement%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-20%2Findia-s-probe-finds-rogue-officials-involved-in-us-murder-plot%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-20%2Findia-s-probe-finds-rogue-officials-involved-in-us-murder-plot%5C%22%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20unnamed%20senior%20officials%20that%20India%20had%20told%20the%20US%20that%20%E2%80%9Crogue%E2%80%9D%20operatives%20not%20authorised%20by%20the%20government%20were%20behind%20the%20alleged%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20claimed%20that%20that%20one%20of%20the%20people%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20plot%20is%20no%20longer%20working%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20external%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%3B%20that%20he%20is%20still%20a%20government%20employee%3B%20and%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20initiated%20criminal%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNew%20Delhi%20has%20informed%20US%20authorities%20about%20the%20findings%20from%20the%20government-appointed%20panel%20set%20up%20to%20probe%20the%20allegations%2C%20the%20people%20said%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bloomberg%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20yet%20to%20publicly%20announce%20that%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20plot%20is%20complete%2C%20or%20even%20offer%20any%20information%20on%20what%20progress%20it%20has%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20after%20the%20Bloomberg%20report%20was%20published%2C%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20India%20said%20it%20had%20nothing%20to%20share%20now.%20The%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20did%20not%20yet%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20state%20department%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fbriefings%2Fdepartment-press-briefing-december-4-2023%2F%23post-507198-INDIALAWENFORCEMENT%5C%22%3Epreviously%20said%20it%20looked%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20seeing%20the%20result%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20into%20the%20allegations%2C%20though%20the%20US%20government%20has%20not%20shared%20any%20details%20about%20the%20investigation%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20prosecutors%20had%20also%20linked%20the%20alleged%20murder%20plot%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada%20last%20year%20in%20their%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20gunned%20to%20death%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20near%20Vancouver.%20He%20too%20was%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20alleged%20in%20public%20last%20year%20that%20his%20government%20had%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20to%20believe%20that%20Indian%20government%20agents%20were%20involved%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20triggered%20a%20diplomatic%20row%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20over%2040%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20restrictions%20on%20Indian%20visas%20for%20Canadian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20asserted%20it%20is%20not%20cooperating%20with%20Canada%20in%20the%20investigation%20into%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20said%20%E2%80%9Cit%20would%20be%20extremely%20difficult%E2%80%9D%20for%20India%20to%20help%20unless%20Canadian%20authorities%20shared%20%E2%80%9Crelevant%20and%20specific%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20with%20their%20Indian%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20republished%20with%20new%20information%20at%2012%3A55%20am%20on%20March%2021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710962735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Frogue-indian-government-operatives-were-involved-in-plot-to-kill-gurpatwant-pannun-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20government%20officials%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20people%20directly%20involved%20is%20still%20employed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20does%20not%20yet%20face%20any%20criminal%20action%2C%20Bloomberg%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Frogue-indian-government-operatives-were-involved-in-plot-to-kill-gurpatwant-pannun-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Secret%20Mall%20Apartment%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Offbeat%20SXSW%20Doc%20Is%20a%20Nice%20Place%20to%20Visit%2C%20but%20You%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20Want%20to%20Live%20There%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710962374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSecret-Mall-Apartment.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235947132%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20solutions%20to%20the%20housing%20crisis%20are%20more%20creative%20than%20others.%20For%20a%20group%20of%20artists%20in%20Providence%2C%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20that%20idea%20was%20put%20to%20the%20test%20when%20they%20infiltrated%20and%20inhabited%20a%20hidden%20alcove%20in%