%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimultaneously%2C%20India%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20major%20purchasers%20of%20crude%20oil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20Russia%20has%20now%20become%20the%20top%20supplier%20of%20crude%20oil%20to%20India%2C%20accounting%20for%20nearly%20one-third%20of%20its%20imports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20India%20has%20also%20increased%20its%20export%20of%20refined%20crude%20to%20Europe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feurope-bought-russian-oil-via-india-at-record-rates-in-2023-despite-ukraine-war%2Farticleshow%2F106777423.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20over%20115%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20the%20same%20period%20when%20the%20continent%20has%20stopped%20all%20economic%20activity%20with%20Moscow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20two%20hours%20later%2C%20Modi%20tweeted%20that%20he%20also%20had%20a%20telephone%20conversation%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHad%20a%20good%20conversation%20with%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZelenskyyUa%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ZelenskyyUa%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20strengthening%20the%20India-Ukraine%20partnership.%20Conveyed%20India%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20support%20for%20all%20efforts%20for%20peace%20and%20bringing%20an%20early%20end%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20humanitarian%20assistance%20guided%20by%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1770427197456634364%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CConveyed%20India%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20support%20for%20all%20efforts%20for%20peace%20and%20bringing%20an%20early%20end%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20humanitarian%20assistance%20guided%20by%20our%20people-centric%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20press%20note%20further%20added%20that%20New%20Delhi%20also%20told%20Ukraine%20about%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20as%20the%20way%20forward%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20highlighted%20that%20India%20supports%20all%20efforts%20for%20an%20early%20and%20peaceful%20resolution%20of%20all%20issues%20between%20the%20Parties.%20He%20added%20that%20India%20would%20continue%20to%20do%20everything%20within%20its%20means%20to%20support%20a%20peaceful%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37725%2FPrime%2BMinister%2BNarendra%2BModi%2Bspeaks%2Bwith%2BPresident%2Bof%2BUkraine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20the%20external%20affairs%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20president%20mentioned%20that%20he%20hoped%20that%20India%20would%20attend%20a%20%E2%80%98global%E2%80%99%20peace%20summit%20planned%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Switzerland%20later%20this%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20be%20important%20for%20us%20to%20see%20India%20attend%20the%20inaugural%20Peace%20Summit%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20being%20prepared%20in%20Switzerland%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20forthcoming%20visit%20of%20the%20foreign%20minister%20to%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20discussed%20the%20development%20of%20our%20bilateral%2