t%20know%20much%20about%20the%20momos%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20try%20it%20out.%20Once%20they%20sampled%20it%2C%20they%20would%20return%20for%20some%20more.%20We%20developed%20a%20small%20fan%20base%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20that%20the%20idea%20would%20do%20well%2C%20the%20duo%20bought%20a%20food%20truck%20and%20started%20a%20business%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20add%20that%20they%20continue%20to%20serve%20momos%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20food%20festival%20in%20New%20York%20that%20runs%20from%20April%20through%20October.%20To%20cater%20to%20every%20diaspora%2C%20the%20menu%20is%20divided%20into%20subtle%20options.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20butter%20garlic%20momos%20are%20a%20hit%20with%20the%20Americans%20while%20the%20spicier%20options%20suit%20the%20Indian%20palate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20emphasise%2C%20however%2C%20that%20perfecting%20the%20momo%20recipe%20has%20been%20a%20challenge.%20Eight%20months%20of%20experimenting%20finally%20led%20them%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20momo%20that%20had%20the%20ideal%20wrapper%20size%2C%20one%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20too%20chewy%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20thick%20enough%20to%20hold%20the%20herbs%20and%20spices%20and%20veggies%2C%20and%20of%20course%20a%20momo%20that%20ticked%20all%20the%20boxes%20for%20taste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20been%20telling.%20As%20the%20clock%20strikes%205%20pm%2C%20Ankita%20and%20Impreet%20brace%20themselves%20for%20the%20office%20crowd%20that%20will%20soon%20be%20stopping%20at%20the%20food%20truck%20for%20their%20snack.%20The%20sizzles%20and%20chopping%20sounds%20travel%20through%20the%20call%20as%20they%20prepare%20the%20fillings%20for%20the%20momos%20for%20the%20hungry%20customers%20who%20will%20soon%20be%20there.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710943576000%2C%22visual%22%3