ligious%20minorities.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fkerala%2Flok-sabha-elections-ldf-attacks-pm-modi-over-alleged-sidelining-of-lone-bjp-muslim-face-in-kerala-from-roadshow%2F%5C%22%3ESalam%20refuted%20the%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20his%20constituency%20did%20not%20have%20any%20connection%20with%20Palakkad%20district%2C%20adding%20that%20that%20the%20Ponnani%20candidate%2C%20Niveditha%20Subramanian%2C%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20roadshow%20as%20the%20Ponnani%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20also%20includes%20the%20Thrithala%20assembly%20segment%20of%20Palakkad%20district.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20heard%20some%20candidates%20were%20going%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20roadshow.%20I%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20it.%20I%20did%20not%20go%20there%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20roadshow.%20I%20went%20there%20to%20meet%20Modi%20and%20invited%20him%20to%20Malappuram%2C%20Salam%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fkerala%2Flok-sabha-elections-ldf-attacks-pm-modi-over-alleged-sidelining-of-lone-bjp-muslim-face-in-kerala-from-roadshow%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fkerala%2Flok-sabha-elections-ldf-attacks-pm-modi-over-alleged-sidelining-of-lone-bjp-muslim-face-in-kerala-from-roadshow%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Subramanian%20had%20invited%20him%20to%20board%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20open%20roof%20vehicle%20but%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20security%20staff%20said%20his%20name%20was%20not%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFurthermore%2C%20the%20vehicle%20was%20already%20full.%20So%2C%20I%20saw%20no%20point%20in%20arguing%20over%20the%20issue%20there.%20Sure%2C%20I%20admit%2C%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20to