ons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20where%20everybody%20works.%20My%20father%20runs%20educational%20institutions%20and%C2%A0%20everyone%20has%20a%20tremendous%20drive%2C%20working%20day%20in%2C%20day%20out.%20I%20have%20been%20visiting%20their%20workplaces%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid%20and%20I%20used%20to%20enjoy%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20an%20acumen%20for%20business%20was%20almost%20ingrained%20in%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20training%20also%20helped%20the%20youngster%20face%20challenges%20when%20people%20refused%20to%20take%20her%20seriously.%20She%20even%20struggled%20to%20find%20employees%20when%20she%20started%20off%2C%20but%20she%20made%20her%20work%20speak%20loud%20and%20clear%2C%20and%20found%20people%20who%20understood%20her%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20this%2C%20she%20also%20runs%20a%20podcast%20called%20%E2%80%98Legally%20Speaking%20With%20Rest%20The%20Case%E2%80%99%20that%20discusses%20latest%20legal%20developments%20and%20decodes%20the%20intricacies%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20there%20any%20legal%20advice%20that%20she%20would%20give%20to%20everyone%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20laws%20that%20concern%20you.%20Legal%20knowledge%20is%20just%20as%20important%20as%20financial%20education.%20As%20consumers%2C%20being%20aware%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344779%2Fworld-consumers-rights-day-landmark-judgements-consumer-law-in-india-online-orders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance.%20Read%20up%20on%20things%20related%20to%20you%20and%20your%20line%20of%20work.%20Know%20your%20rights%20as%20a%20tenant%20or%20property%20owner%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Pictures%20Courtesy%20Shreya%20Sharma)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C