%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fdemand-for-us-blueberry-rising-in-india%2Farticle34852525.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSHBC%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20imports%20of%20blueberries%20in%20fresh%20and%20dried%20forms%20grew%20from%20almost%20zero%20in%202009%20to%201%2C900%20tonnes%20in%202020%2C%20making%20India%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20top%20importers%20of%20blueberries.%20This%20trade%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20India%20is%20growing%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20around%2030%20percent%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20numbers%20are%20rising%20annually%2C%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Keya%20Salot%20has%20stepped%20up%20to%20bring%20these%20numbers%20down%20to%20some%20extent.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202021-22%2C%20India%20was%20importing%20%242.2%20billion%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313743%2Fchethan-shetty-quit-corporate-job-to-become-farmer-in-bellare-mangaluru-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20vegetables.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20really%20a%20good%20number.%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20the%20sector%20to%20cultivate%20these%20exotic%20varieties%20locally.%20By%20doing%20this%2C%20it%20would%20also%20make%20them%20affordable%20for%20consumers%20beyond%20metros%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20these%20exotic%20berries.%20Today%2C%20she%20has%20scaled%20up%20the%20production%20on%2020%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20estimates%20a%20production%20of%20at%20least%20135%20tonnes%20of%20berries%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th