%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20required%20to%20protect%20crops%20like%20raspberries%20and%20blueberries%20from%20extreme%20temperatures.%20Currently%2C%20India%20only%20has%20poly%20houses%20as%20an%20infrastructure%20for%20protected%20cultivation%2C%20and%20in%20geographical%20climates%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20we%20need%20protection%20from%20harsh%20conditions%20rather%20than%20adding%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20developed%20our%20own%20low-cost%20tunnel%20structures%20for%20growing%20these%20berries%20where%20we%20can%20add%20or%20remove%20the%20plastic%20cover%20as%20per%20the%20weather%20requirements%20and%20maintain%20ideal%20temperature%20conditions%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20plants.%20With%20this%2C%20we%20can%20now%20provide%20a%20warmer%20climate%20during%20the%20winter%20nights%20and%20cooler%20conditions%20for%20growth%20during%20the%20summer%20days%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20protecting%20the%20crops%20from%20rain.%20This%20technique%20has%20its%20origin%20in%20the%20European%20countries%20where%20they%20use%20the%20structure%20to%20protect%20the%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeya%20installed%20low-cost%20tunnels%20in%20about%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20farm%20and%20is%20cultivating%20at%20least%20seven%20varieties%20of%20exotic%20berries.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343071%2Fhow-to-grow-strawberries-dragon-fruit-turmeric-terrace-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrowing%20blueberries%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20high%20tunnels%20protects%20them%20from%20extremes%20of%20temperature%2C%20requires%20less%20water%2C%20and%20yields%20more%20fruit.%20This%20method%20also%20helps%20blueberries%20ripen%20earlier.%20Instead%20of%20the%20usual%20harvest%20period%20that%20lasts%20only%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20we%20can%20harvest%20yields%20for%20four%20to%20five%20months%20with%20this%20method%2C%E2%80%9D