age%E2%80%99s%20art%20over%20time.%20Her%20effort%20to%20take%20Oraon%20paintings%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20Madhubani%20or%20Gond%20started%2015%20years%20ago.%20She%20pioneered%20the%20transition%20of%20these%20paintings%20from%20walls%20to%20cloth%20and%20handmade%20paper.%20Today%2C%20her%20artworks%20have%20journeyed%20across%20India%2C%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20to%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20with%20a%20tribal%20art%20fair%20workshop%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20organised%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Rashtriya%20Manav%20Sangrahalaya.%20We%20only%20sold%20one%20painting%2C%20but%20it%20gave%20us%20hope%20that%20if%20done%20correctly%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20viable%20option.%20A%20few%20years%20into%20doing%20exhibitions%20and%20local%20%3Cem%3Ehaats%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20learnt%20about%20Samvaad.%20I%20joined%20the%20initiative%20as%20a%20fellow.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20fellowship%2C%20I%20released%20an%20art%20curation%20book%20titled%20%E2%80%98Evam%20Kala%E2%80%99%20on%20Oraon%20folklore%2C%20documenting%20the%20culture%20and%20traditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sumanti%2C%20who%20has%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20political%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20that%20she%20also%20attends%20handicraft%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344526%2Fsamvaad-tata-steel-foundation-celebrates-culture-of-tribes-of-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eart%20workshops%20by%20Samvaa%3C%2Fa%3Ed%20to%20learn%20about%20new%20market%20trends%20and%20skills%20that%20can%20help%20her%20with%20more%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20in%20an%20exhibition%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20more%20than%20just%20selling%20the%20paintings.%20I%20learnt%20that%20if%20you%20wear%20traditional%20clothing%20in%20exhibitions%2C%20more%20people%20tend%20to%20visit%20your%20stall.%20The%20way%2